{
  "annotations": {
    "list": []
  },
  "description": "Monitors the Redis-backed global concurrency guard for Milvus — slot usage, wait times, timeouts, and fallback status across all 6 database services.",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "links": [],
  "panels": [
    {
      "title": "How to Use This Dashboard",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "id": 100,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Tuning Guide\n- **RAM climbing?** → Check *Slots Active* — lower `MILVUS_GLOBAL_MAX_CONCURRENT` in `.env`\n- **Ingestion slow?** → Check *Timeouts* — raise `MILVUS_WRITE_CEILING` if RAM allows\n- **Search latency?** → Check *Acquire Duration* for Tier 1 — lower `MILVUS_WRITE_CEILING`\n- **Fallback active?** → Redis is down — guard is in local-only mode, no cross-service coordination"
      }
    },
    {
      "title": "Slots Active by Tier",
      "description": "Current Milvus operations in flight, stacked by tier. Compare against the threshold lines.",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 4 },
      "id": 1,
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 30,
            "stacking": { "mode": "normal", "group": "A" },
            "lineWidth": 2
          },
          "unit": "short",
          "min": 0
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Global Max" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "custom.drawStyle", "value": "line" },
              { "id": "custom.fillOpacity", "value": 0 },
              { "id": "custom.lineStyle", "value": { "fill": "dash", "dash": [10, 10] } },
              { "id": "custom.stacking", "value": { "mode": "none" } },
              { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "red" } },
              { "id": "custom.lineWidth", "value": 2 }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Write Ceiling" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "custom.drawStyle", "value": "line" },
              { "id": "custom.fillOpacity", "value": 0 },
              { "id": "custom.lineStyle", "value": { "fill": "dash", "dash": [10, 10] } },
              { "id": "custom.stacking", "value": { "mode": "none" } },
              { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "orange" } },
              { "id": "custom.lineWidth", "value": 2 }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Tier 1 — Search" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "blue" } }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Tier 2 — High Writes" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "orange" } }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Tier 3 — Low Writes" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "semi-dark-green" } }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(milvus_guard_slots_active{tier=\"1\"})",
          "legendFormat": "Tier 1 — Search",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "sum(milvus_guard_slots_active{tier=\"2\"})",
          "legendFormat": "Tier 2 — High Writes",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "expr": "sum(milvus_guard_slots_active{tier=\"3\"})",
          "legendFormat": "Tier 3 — Low Writes",
          "refId": "C"
        },
        {
          "expr": "milvus_guard_slots_max",
          "legendFormat": "Global Max",
          "refId": "D"
        },
        {
          "expr": "milvus_guard_write_ceiling",
          "legendFormat": "Write Ceiling",
          "refId": "E"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Slots by Service (Detail)",
      "description": "Which service is consuming the most slots right now.",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 4 },
      "id": 2,
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 20,
            "stacking": { "mode": "normal", "group": "A" },
            "lineWidth": 1
          },
          "unit": "short",
          "min": 0
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "milvus_guard_slots_active",
          "legendFormat": "{{service}} (tier {{tier}})",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Acquire Duration p95",
      "description": "How long services wait for a slot. Tier 1 (search) > 2s = problem. Writers > 5s = starving.",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 14 },
      "id": 3,
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "lineWidth": 2
          },
          "unit": "s",
          "min": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 2 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 5 }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le, tier) (rate(milvus_guard_acquire_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "Tier {{tier}} p95",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, sum by (le, tier) (rate(milvus_guard_acquire_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "Tier {{tier}} p50",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Acquire Timeouts Rate",
      "description": "How often services fail to get a slot. Sustained > 0 = pool too small or tier starved.",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 14 },
      "id": 4,
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "bars",
            "fillOpacity": 50,
            "lineWidth": 1
          },
          "unit": "ops",
          "min": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "red", "value": 0.01 }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (service) (rate(milvus_guard_acquire_timeouts_total[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{service}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Fallback Active",
      "description": "1 = Redis is down, guard running in local-only mode. No cross-service coordination.",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 22 },
      "id": 5,
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [
            { "type": "value", "options": { "0": { "text": "OK", "color": "green" } } },
            { "type": "value", "options": { "1": { "text": "FALLBACK", "color": "red" } } }
          ],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "red", "value": 1 }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "max(milvus_guard_fallback_active)",
          "legendFormat": "Fallback",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Lease Expirations",
      "description": "Slots auto-released due to crashes or ops exceeding TTL. Should be 0 in healthy state.",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 22 },
      "id": 6,
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "bars",
            "fillOpacity": 50
          },
          "unit": "short",
          "min": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "red", "value": 0.01 }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (service) (rate(milvus_guard_lease_expirations_total[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{service}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Current Config",
      "description": "Live values of MILVUS_GLOBAL_MAX_CONCURRENT and MILVUS_WRITE_CEILING.",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 22 },
      "id": 7,
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "blue", "value": null }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "milvus_guard_slots_max",
          "legendFormat": "Global Max",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "milvus_guard_write_ceiling",
          "legendFormat": "Write Ceiling",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Total Slots Used (Gauge)",
      "description": "Current total slot usage as a percentage of the global max.",
      "type": "gauge",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 22 },
      "id": 8,
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 1,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 0.7 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 0.9 }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(milvus_guard_slots_active) / milvus_guard_slots_max",
          "legendFormat": "Pool Usage",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Pipeline Processing Duration (comparison)",
      "description": "End-to-end message processing time from the existing metric. Compare with guard acquire duration to identify bottleneck.",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 26 },
      "id": 9,
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "lineWidth": 1
          },
          "unit": "s",
          "min": 0
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le, service_name) (rate(pipeline_processing_duration_seconds_bucket{service_name=~\".*database.*\"}[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "{{service_name}} p95",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "refresh": "10s",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "tags": ["milvus", "concurrency", "guard", "rag-hp"],
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "DS_PROMETHEUS",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "prometheus",
        "current": { "text": "Prometheus", "value": "Prometheus" }
      }
    ]
  },
  "time": { "from": "now-1h", "to": "now" },
  "timepicker": {},
  "timezone": "browser",
  "title": "Milvus Concurrency Guard",
  "uid": "milvus-concurrency-guard",
  "version": 1
}